/author-Hf6X05OHar6QeIUMVbfHuw">Hướng Tử Nhân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Ph%C3%A1c/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%BAc/poem-SHato7hti_kk6NTDzvifYA">Tái hạ khúc - 塞下曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Ph%C3%A1c/author-AGCqPCIFskZR14TGi3NQzg">Chu Phác</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-bQ477RcBYD7f-2jwyhfNig">Tái hạ khúc kỳ 2 - 塞下曲其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-xOkIiHqP9P6nrS8jJbgRNg">Thường Kiến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%A7n-trung-ng%C3%A2m-k%E1%BB%B3-10-M%C3%A3i-hoa/poem-_4gk5x-gykPP-i6yeC1YUQ">Tần trung ngâm kỳ 10 - Mãi hoa - 秦中吟其十－買花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/T%E1%BB%91ng-Giang-tham-qu%C3%A2n-ho%C3%A0n-Kim-L%C4%83ng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-uxaYcM0W4yFbdWyqO0NoUg">Tống Giang tham quân hoàn Kim Lăng kỳ 1 - 送江參軍還金陵其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/X%C3%A0-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-OTOkL6TRbM0V41YwHIzvfA">Xà Tường</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
